name: Khamroz Abdukhoshimov
text: I love their spaghetti and spinach stromboli. Guys working there are super friendly and helpful. Prices are decent and the place is always clean. There is all-you-can drinks, mostly cold drink. I’m vegetarian and they offer some vegetarian …More

name: Jessica Ashley
text: Fresh, hot, and ready. Great selection of good choices. Good price, clean, and friendly staff.

name: John Taylor
text: Great staff. They always see me coming and know what I want. Even when I don't visit in a while.

name: G Kemp III
text: The food is pretty good, but it's crazy expensive. It's way cheaper to buy a whole pizza from here than by the slice.
